ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天光咪有返regular巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1285ef1674d7b07ee4a3df9a320478b8d942ea08","tid":435943,"uid":144975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭n車都未必架架近屋企啦？</blockquote><br />\n咁揸n車嗰個點返屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸n車嘅應該揸到清晨先放工啦，咁就有普通線歸家"},{"pid":"8f4719b863b2417f8b49daebc1a56502855e5db2","tid":435943,"uid":672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"的士"},{"pid":"98055b5ece0bf3b2cf024dc9248539feef174e1b","tid":435943,"uid":144975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士</blockquote><br />\n晚晚咁搭法300蚊交通津貼都唔夠玩啦？唔可持續發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302625515ba1fded38c6fb822da6191f5c1235e2","tid":435943,"uid":144975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"有無行內人答吓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aef9dec62a5777ba7f6917aa7bcea30e160fd8f","tid":435943,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed7b99148b41df7403cca8fb0abd5fea1cd0448","tid":435943,"uid":22309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"有工程車"},{"pid":"0d7d6495b3df13ea1e99e73c99fd4a2b68dc4607","tid":435943,"uid":94501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有員工接駁車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁員工接駁車司機點番屋企？"},{"pid":"f3e4391d7fe6c233e5e75f20f311004faf8ff89b","tid":435943,"uid":144975,"like":1,"dislike":0,